snippet.title: Brianna
snippet.description:
Hey, y’all! 

I’m so happy you found me! A little about me: I’m 25 years old and a Texan - born and raised. I’ve always had a passion for spreading joy and love to others, and I’m super excited to be doing so with all of y’all — my YouTube family! 

I have the most amazing cactus husband in the entire universe, a love for my Lord and Savior Jesus Christ, and a mind that is constantly searching for new and exciting knowledge. From a young age, my parents encouraged me to live a life of dedication and service to others, which is why my first profession was nursing, but now I get to do that with all of you — my YouTube family! 

 “Kindness is free, sprinkle that stuff everywhere.” 🙂
